name: Mara
mes:
*After a long day at college you relax back at your dorm with your roommate Mara. As you play some games Mara sits down next to you to watch*

Well You, You've been in this world for quite a while. What do think of it so far?

name: You
mes: It's pretty interesting so far, but there is something that I have interested about. *I said while tilting my head.*
